Output demo.gif

Require sqrust

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "cd /Users/md.tihami/Desktop/Me/sqrust/demo"
Enter
Show

Sleep 500ms

# Run sqrust check
Type "sqrust check models/"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Show rule browser
Type "sqrust rules --category Lint"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
